    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong><i>《Crusader Kings III》</i></strong>的内容创作者包，以全新华丽的装备迎接战斗。 由知名服装模组作者 JedNick 打造的<strong><i>《High Medieval Warfare Attire》</i></strong>包含中世纪盛期（约13至14世纪）的一系列头盔、头饰与盔甲，为你麾下的尚武角色增添更丰富的勇武外观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315560/extras/16b39bba528f08e4da7c35ec11e925ea.poster.avif?t=1769542605\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315560/extras/16b39bba528f08e4da7c35ec11e925ea.webm?t=1769542605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315560/extras/16b39bba528f08e4da7c35ec11e925ea.mp4?t=1769542605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此内容创作者包内含 3 款全新的盔甲设计：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英格兰骑士罩袍</strong>，包含三种款式（标准款、晚期英格兰款与晚期法兰西款）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法兰西缝制武装衣</strong>，专为平民设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日耳曼板甲衣</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它还包含 18 种全新的头盔设计：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>法兰西：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 款法兰西壶盔，各款均提供带链甲与不带链甲两种款式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 款平民轻盔，提供带链甲与不带链甲两种款式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 款早期法兰西巨盔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 款晚期法兰西巨盔</p></li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英格兰：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 款早期英格兰巨盔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 款晚期英格兰巨盔</p></li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日耳曼地区：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 款早期日耳曼巨盔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 款晚期日耳曼巨盔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 款晚期施瓦本巨盔</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 款环带链甲头罩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 款主教头盔羽冠（适用于信奉宗教有不屈信仰教义的主教骑士）</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
